did.head: DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY
did.repository: Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library
did.abstract: The collection contains travel guides, road maps, brochures, leaflets, post cards, and souvenir publications relating to various states of the United States and foreign countries all around the world.

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: The collection contains travel guides, road maps, brochures, leaflets, post cards, and souvenir publications relating to various states of the United States and foreign countries all around the world.
